Following is a list of most useful c++ idioms
@see http://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/More_C++_Idioms

0.Interface Class       => Separating an interface of a class from its implementation

1.RAII                  => Resource Acquisition Is Initialization

2.Pimpl                 => Pointer To Implementation

3.Checked delete        => Increase safety of delete expression

4.Virtual Constructor   => Creating an object or it's copy without knowing its concrete type
